      "note": "off-camera: stage the shared persisted rail preference expanded so Automation reads with its label. .wc-rail-panel-toggle is the same control both ways (probe-verified July 11: expanded shows 'Hide panel', Automation link width>200). Skipped when already expanded. No submenu toggle is needed: on mkt-automation.html the Marketing group is the active module and its submenu (Campaigns/Automation) is rendered open by default."
